    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so permanent though. like no matter what i do or how much i try to ignore them, the feeling that i'm just this unwanted person stays the same. it's not even a \"rough patch\" anymore, it's just who i am to everyone. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery and there's literally no point in trying to fix something that's just fundamentally broken.",
