      "content": "i know... but it's not just about my worth. it's about the noise. it's just constant. i feel like i'm constantly running from something that's already won. i just want the noise to stop. i want to actually be able to find some peace where people can't reach me anymore. like, is there even any way to just... exit this situation for good?",
